title: Kirk Minihane Hosts the First Annual Steve Robinson Red Hot Dog Eating Contest
description:
The day we've all been waiting for: The long promised hot dog eating contest. Will Steve Robinson prove himself or will the house of lies he's built come crashing down? But first: Minihane's old sports radio competitors stepped up to question a Boston Globe columnist about his paper's flagrant hypocrisy on the Antonio Brown story and KFC proves he's truly fallen down the Minifan rabbit hole.Â 


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
